IDB Donates $16 Million to Finance Bahraini Project

-- B y   S a r a h   A b d u l l a h
-- 
2011-07-12T17:32:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/idb-donates-16-million-to-finance-bahraini-project.html
The  Islamic Development Bank  has
announced the donation of $16 million for the construction of a
mixed-use project in the Bahraini capital of Manama.  The 13-floor project will include a mall, hotel and
residential apartments and is being financed by the IDB through
the Bahrain-based Al Jafaria Endowment Fund, according to an e-
mail statement from the IDB today.  The Jeddah-based bank has been supporting endowments to
finance projects in 20 Muslim countries since 1997 and has
donated a total of $884 million over the past fourteen years,
the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
